---
title: Saucy Indian-Spiced Chicken with Coconut Rice and Peas
description: This fusion curry dish hits all the right notes! Cool, creamy coconut milk rice and sweet green peas are the perfect flavour match for warming tikka sauce and juicy spiced chicken breasts. You'll be licking the plate clean!
